{"tid":614160,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[十萬火急] 買左阿聯酋航空 機票打漏英文名","createTime":"2018-04-02T09:26:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T11:08:03.000Z","uid":101068,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4af356ec0d99751d8606948e7df411f08fd4da1f","tid":614160,"uid":101068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T09:26:34.000Z","msg":"因為我係經expedia連機票酒店一齊買 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n琴日先發現朋友張機票個名打漏左個英文名(佢身份證有加英文名) <br />\n而因為我經expedia買 佢都寫到明張機票係economy saver 姐係無得上&rdquo;管理預訂&rdquo;改個人資料 阿聯酋官網都話機票無得改名 只可取消機票重新買過<br />\n今日我都打左去expedia問 佢話會sd啲資料去阿聯酋個邊 但佢唔清楚係可以補錢定要重新買過 加上阿聯酋休公眾假期 姐係最快都要聽日先有人回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請問有無巴打試過呢個情況 因為我今個星期五就飛 好驚唔夠時間處理 跪求各位巴打解答"},{"pid":"f1becd2754195f2d02277df0dbcb720d84f28a53","tid":614160,"uid":21120,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T09:33:07.000Z","msg":"唔使改<br />\n一定上到機"},{"pid":"5b94688b5dc626e09c34a76a1a8e6c45568eee5f","tid":614160,"uid":101068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T09:57:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfeb96a8abb569cdc4bf8a7b534e9538cd33d978","tid":614160,"uid":11072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T09:58:23.000Z","msg":"攞塗改液塗左護照個英文名"},{"pid":"c52a1068ead53fa3d92b214a98045b414aa5a8d6","tid":614160,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T09:58:43.000Z","msg":"要睇下你夠唔夠靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e54dea756c0141a23086277b0b9c36b6cf7dec7f","tid":614160,"uid":137275,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:15:11.000Z","msg":"果陣去歐洲都係填漏英文名<br />\n所以我改埋passport 同身份證都無英文名<br />\n果陣搭business 買左2皮幾野廢時博<br />\n所以我比千幾蚊改哂證件名 <br />\n<br />\n之前扒過文有人話上到機有人話試過上唔到"},{"pid":"fe7